+ *
+ * Routines for TuxOnIce's user interface.
+ *
+ * The user interface code talks to a userspace program via a
+ * netlink socket.
+ *
+ * The kernel side:
+ * - starts the userui program;
+ * - sends text messages and progress bar status;
+ *
